Spy Streak:

     He launched a couple of missles at the hole in
the wall and transformed to follow. He was small
enough to fit inside the base without problem, he
quickly caught up to the bot.
     "We will speak," He yelled to the bot. He had
already locked onto the bot with his missles, but
didn't fire them yet.
